"{\"uid\": \"upr.org-utah-news-2024-04-11-thursday-am-headlines-uta-announces-transit-expansion-for-potential-2034-utah-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Utah's four republican candidates for attorney general gathered for a debate on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 90, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 4, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"score\": 0.9999999767542251, \"rank\": 2.3244035918011947e-08, \"text\": \"Utah\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The debate was held at the SCERA Center for the Arts in Orem and was hosted by the Utah Eagle Forum.\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 175, \"end\": 179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"score\": 0.9999999767542251, \"rank\": 2.3244035918011947e-08, \"text\": \"Utah\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\"}, {\"begin\": 180, \"end\": 191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eagle_Forum\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eagle Forum\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eagle_Forum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eagle_Forum\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The candidates spoke to a crowd of around 300 republican state delegates.\", \"from\": 193, \"to\": 266, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Though the candidates shared similar opinions on abortion, illegal immigration, federal involvement in land use and education, the focus of the debate was on the differences in how they hope to serve.\", \"from\": 268, \"to\": 468, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The candidates included were former lawmaker and legislative chief of staff Derek Brown, former assistant attorney general Frank Mylar, Utah Division of Risk Management director Rachel Terry and former Zions Bank vice president