\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brenner_Pass\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brenner was described as a \\\"squatter\\\" who lived near Rounds when he disappeared.\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1315, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Utah Transit Authority announced it has plans to expand and redesign Utah's transit in time for the possible 2034 Olympic Games in Salt Lake City.\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1467, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1321, \"end\": 1343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Transit_Authority\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Utah Transit Authority\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Transit_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Transit_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 1390, \"end\": 1394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"score\": 0.9999999767542251, \"rank\": 2.3244035918011947e-08, \"text\": \"Utah\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\"}, {\"begin\": 1452, \"end\": 1466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"score\": 0.9999991155354383, \"rank\": 8.844652213815176e-07, \"text\": \"Salt Lake City\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The plans include a new Orange line of the TRAX running from the Salt Lake City airport to the University of Utah.\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1493, \"end\": 1499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orange_S.A.\", \"score\": 0.7459867356549612, \"rank\": 0.3405064087373202, \"text\": \"Orange\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orange_S.A.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orange_S.A.\"}, {\"begin\": 1534, \"end\": 1556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City_International_